{"tid":1736461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲 真係我地既生神仙","createTime":"2019-11-18T17:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T02:16:25.000Z","uid":174207,"like":6,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c8172b2d8e91c94b5ce1c9bb4103cc09d9ec10c4","tid":1736461,"uid":174207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:58:30.000Z","msg":"陳雲 真係我地既生神仙"},{"pid":"55f9ba7fd0b508002dc0f99033882e2f580a05dc","tid":1736461,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8172b2d8e91c94b5ce1c9bb4103cc09d9ec10c4","tid":1736461,"uid":174207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:58:30.000Z","msg":"陳雲 真係我地既生神仙"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:00:10.000Z","msg":"幫推  借位一用<br />\n<br />\n我呼籲 政治人物 校長 社工 行入去警總叫曾經濫捕 拳打腳踢 插贓 嘅警察自首<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1736095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1736095</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老鼠曾<br />\n<br />\n如果你地唔夠膽咁做 根本係雙重標準<br />\n乜撚野中學校長都只係助紂為虐<br />\n我屌你 再你埋你間中學<br />\n<br />\n重可以有隨行傳媒同假傳媒跟住入去<br />\n<br />\n藍衫可以先摘名 記低UI<br />\n白衫就要捉住遊街 公審<br />\n<br />\n但校長 社工可以確保佢唔被濫用暴力 虐打<br />\n享有呢d本身香港基本法已經清楚寫明 每個人都有嘅莊嚴承諾嘅權利<br />\n<br />\n題外話 <br />\n雙普選都係基本法清楚寫明 每個人都有嘅莊嚴承諾嘅權利<br />\n但都唔知去咗邊到"},{"pid":"4b6d0277b3afd8524e2321d018fbab43ba75fde9","tid":1736461,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:01:25.000Z","msg":"死開啦⋯⋯青山騎牆派！"},{"pid":"fb955e0e3c4a00fc0fd1136fdb786dda76f679e5","tid":1736461,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:01:34.000Z","msg":"[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0d8cf9e52b6dc536e76eaa40f66bc041ff603c4f","tid":1736461,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:03:35.000Z","msg":"冇料到 蕭生有用好多"},{"pid":"d91bd0596100295f30f14d2098a05854c87888f5","tid":1736461,"uid"